<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARTH DAY FOCUSES ATTENTION ON DETERIORATION OF ENVIRONMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Society's current environmental consciousness is proof again that the American 
liberal political agenda is decades ahead of its time. 
</P>
<P>
Liberals were promoting environmentalism 30 years ago, when the status quo 
labeled them as "loonies." In fact, liberals throughout history have 
consistently promoted causes and issues that eventually became part of the 
American mainstream. Racial and sexual equality, opposition to the Vietnam War 
and warnings over the dangers of nuclear power are only some of the issues 
initially championed by liberals. 
</P>
<P>
So take heart, liberals, your cause today will become the norm of political 
thought tomorrow. 
</P>
<P>
RON KOBAYASHI 
</P>
<P>
Tustin 
</P>
</TEXT>
