NORTHROP UNITS IN DEAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Northrop Corp.'s divisions in Anaheim and Hawthorne won contracts totaling 
$20.6 million from the Army to supply fire control equipment 
</P>
